description: Desirable front-facing 'G stack' home, boasting Back Bay and South End views in a premier full-service boutique building. This upper-level home is the epitome of luxury, featuring numerous high-end upgrades and premium finishes. Chef's kitchen is equipped with Wolf and Sub Zero appliances and sleek European cabinetry. Retreat to the primary bedroom, where a spacious walk-in closet and en suite bath with a double vanity awaits. The king-sized 2nd bedroom, in-unit laundry, generous closets, and a walkout deck provide additional comfort and convenience. Enjoy a host of building amenities including concierge, elevator, gym, pet wash station, on-site restaurant, clubroom and a spectacular common roof deck with gas grills, an outdoor fireplace, and stunning city views. Nestled between the vibrant Seaport and South End neighborhoods, this home offers easy access to public transportation, major highways, shops, and award-winning restaurants.
